<div class="skinny_wrapper topics">
  <h1 id="form_title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <h3>Our Goal</h3>
  <p>Here at Consonancie, our goal is give aspiring writers and jounralists a platform for their work. We aim to connect people through the sharing of ideas, opinions, thoughts, and art.</p>
  <h3 class="title">How should I write my article?</h3>
  <p>Your article can and should reflect your style. It can be funny, serious, informational, etc. If you're into writing about news or politics, that's what your focus should be. However, if you love watching netflix and want to share your favorite shows, write about that! It's best to write about what YOU'RE interested in!</p>
  <h3 class="title">How many pictures should I include?</h3>
  <p>This depends on your article! Pictures are a great way to clarify your point and you can even use pictures and gifs for humor! If you're writing a news article about a celebrity, you should include pictures, embedded tweets, instagram posts, etc. If you're posting funny tweets, it shouldn't have a lot of words. However if you're writing about an experience, pictures are definitely needed, but only a few. </p>
  <h3 class="title">How long should my article be?</h3>
  <p>However long you need to convey your point!</p>
  <h3 class="title">How long will it take for my article to be published?</h3>
  <p>A couple of days at most!</p>
  <h3 class="title">How can I get my article shared on the instagram page?</h3>
  <p>We will try to get as many articles as possible to be shared! To make your article stand out, try to make it unique amd interesting for people to read! We will choose the articles that are the most likely to be clicked on!</p>
